    "title": "こと が ある: Having Experienced",
    "explanation": "A new pattern: [past verb] + ことがある means 'have experienced.' 一回は化け物をみたことがある — have once seen a monster. 鼾をきいたことがある — have experienced hearing snoring.\n\nことがある turns a past event into a claimed life experience.\n\nRe-read and find ことがある. What experiences are being claimed?"
